---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Egypt Alumin & Noel Murphy | Direct European Sales Partner" 
  description="Learn about the strategic partnership connecting advanced primary Egyptian aluminium smelting with direct European B2B logistics. Under the sales leadership of Noel Murphy in Ireland."
  lang="en"
>
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <div class="container">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/en/">Home</a></li>
        <li aria-current="page">About Us</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="product-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="product-hero-grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
        <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Smelting Capacity · Direct Logistics</span>
          <h1>An Egyptian smelter. An Irish sales partner. One supply chain with no gaps.</h1>
          <p class="product-hero-lead" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">
            Combining 50,000 m² of advanced industrial smelting capacity with localized, 
            rapid B2B supply chain oversight led by Noel Murphy.
          </p>
          <div class="product-hero-badges" style="justify-content: center; margin-top: 1.8rem;">
            <span>50,000 m² Smelting Facility</span>
            <span>Hydro-Powered Production</span>
            <span>Direct Sea Routes to EU</span>
            <span>Irish Sales Office</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       THE PARTNERSHIP
       ============================================================ -->
  <section id="facility" style="background: var(--white); padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cbam-inner" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center;">
        <div class="product-image" style="box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);">
          <div class="product-img-container-inner" style="border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;">
            <img src="/images/hero/1.3-aluminium-smelter-exterior-egypt-manufacturing-plant.webp" alt="Egypt Alumin Smelter" class="product-img-modern" style="width:100%; object-fit:cover;" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Strategic Industrial Advantage</span>
          <h2>Hydro-Powered Smelting on the Nile</h2>
          <p>
            Egypt Alumin operates an ISO 9001-certified primary smelter and alloy foundry in Egypt.
            Using abundant hydro-electric power generated by the Aswan High Dam, we achieve a highly competitive
            carbon intensity compared to coal-reliant standard smelters.
          </p>
          <p>
            This clean energy baseline gives our European buyers a substantial competitive advantage: lower embedded emissions 
            that minimize regulatory tax liabilities under the EU's Carbon Border Adjustment Mechanism (CBAM).
          </p>
          <p>
            Our facility produces up to 320,000 tonnes of high-quality primary ingots, standard 20kg die-casting alloys, 
            and customized Al-Si formulations annually.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       NOEL MURPHY PROFILE
       ============================================================ -->
  <section id="noel" style="background: var(--silver-soft); padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cbam-inner" style="grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center;">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Direct B2B Supply Partner</span>
          <h2>Meet Noel Murphy</h2>
          <p>
            Securing industrial metal supplies from North Africa requires absolute clarity, rapid response times, and an 
            intimate understanding of European automotive and manufacturing schedules. 
          </p>
          <p>
            Operating from our direct sales office in Ireland, Noel Murphy manages all European inquiries, contract structuring, 
            and custom alloying specifications. He serves as your single point of contact, ensuring that technical requests 
            reach our metallurgists instantly and that shipping logistics proceed without friction.
          </p>
          <blockquote style="border-left: 4px solid var(--teal); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; font-style: italic; color: var(--ink);">
            "Our mission is simple: provide European industrial manufacturing foundries with a reliable, REACH-registered, 
            and CBAM-ready primary aluminium supply chain. No intermediaries, no hidden fees, just direct, high-purity metal."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="product-image" style="box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);">
          <div class="product-img-container-inner" style="border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 1/1;">
            <img src="/images/branding/brand-noel-murphy-portrait-02.webp" alt="Noel Murphy" class="product-img-modern" style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       LOGISTICS FOOTPRINT
       ============================================================ -->
  <section id="logistics" style="background: var(--white); padding: 5rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="text-align:center; max-width:700px; margin: 0 auto 4rem auto;">
        <h2>Unbroken Mediterranean Logistics</h2>
        <p>Our proximity to the Suez Canal and Alexandria ports allows us to deliver high-tonnage containers to major European ports with unmatched transit speed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="product-grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
        <div style="background:var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding:2rem; border-radius:var(--radius-lg); text-align:center;">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif; color:var(--teal); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">10–14 Days</h3>
          <strong>Southern Europe</strong>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem; margin-top:0.5rem; color:var(--ink-soft);">Transit to Genoa (Italy) and Barcelona (Spain).</p>
        </div>

        <div style="background:var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding:2rem; border-radius:var(--radius-lg); text-align:center;">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif; color:var(--teal); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">18–24 Days</h3>
          <strong>Northern Europe</strong>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem; margin-top:0.5rem; color:var(--ink-soft);">Transit to Rotterdam (Netherlands) and Hamburg (Germany).</p>
        </div>

        <div style="background:var(--silver-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding:2rem; border-radius:var(--radius-lg); text-align:center;">
          <h3 style="font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif; color:var(--teal); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">20 t</h3>
          <strong>Minimum MOQ</strong>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem; margin-top:0.5rem; color:var(--ink-soft);">Standard single 20-foot container capacity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       FINAL CTA
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow on-dark">Direct European Sales Office</span>
      <h2>Discuss your metal supply requirements</h2>
      <p>Whether you need a narrowed chemical composition window, customized packaging bundles, or a sample shipment for trial heats, speak directly with Noel Murphy.</p>
      <div class="final-cta-actions">
        <a href="/en/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:+353871187806" class="btn btn-secondary">Call Noel: +353 87 118 7806</a>
      </div>
      <p class="final-cta-direct">
        Direct Email: <a href="mailto:noel@egyptalumin.com">noel@egyptalumin.com</a> · WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/353871187806">Direct Chat</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .product-img-container-inner {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .product-img-modern {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }
  .product-img-container-inner:hover .product-img-modern {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }
</style>
